Package: perioDNA
Type: Package
Title: Probing DNA sequences for periodic oligonucleotides
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jacques Serizay
Maintainer: Jacques Serizay <js2264@cam.ac.uk>
Description: Periodic elements represented in oligosequences. CAUTION: This package is still in pre-alpha phase. The functions in this package provide a straightforward approach to identify local over-represented periodic elements in short sequences such as regulatory elements.  
